            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>伊魯米納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ILMN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ILMN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ILMN-US</a>)截至台北時間20日23:22股價上漲6.32美元，報126.44美元，漲幅5.26%，成交量512,286（股），盤中最高價126.50美元、最低價121.50美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：+1.42%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+1.77%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+2.25%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+2.61%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>伊魯米納(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:ILMN:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/ILMN\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">ILMN-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：-0.01%</li> <li>近 1 月：+22.58%</li> <li>近 3 月：+20.05%</li> <li>近 6 月：+47.04%</li> <li>今年以來：-6.84%</li></ul></section></main>",
